rows.label: bf05090100_0010
rows.name:
Well, I guess it'd be quickest for
me to lead the way from here.

rows.label: bf05090100_0020
rows.name: We just need to get over the ridge, right?

rows.label: bf05090100_0030
rows.name:
Indeed. The delegation from Acedia
will meet us there.

rows.label: bf05090100_0040
rows.name: Roger that!

rows.label: bf05090100_0050
rows.name:
Will leave it to boss!
Lead the way!

rows.label: bf05090100_0055
rows.name: Ha-ha!

rows.label: bf05090100_0060
rows.name:
Don't get an inflated head. We're just
following the islands, you know.

rows.label: bf05090100_0070
rows.name: Hey, it's still dangerous!

rows.label: bf05090100_0080
rows.name:
There's a lot of tough monsters
around these parts.

rows.label: bf05090100_0090
rows.name: Well, I won't deny that...

rows.label: bf05090100_0100
rows.name: So how we going?

rows.label: bf05090100_0110
rows.name: Err...

rows.label: bf05090100_0115
rows.name: What about Iyasaki?

rows.label: bf05090100_0120
rows.name: What about it?

rows.label: bf05090100_0125
rows.name: Will we pass it?

rows.label: bf05090100_0130
rows.name: I mean, we could go that way.

rows.label: bf05090100_0135
rows.name: Let's do it! I mean, let's visit your village!

rows.label: bf05090100_0140
rows.name: Okay, calm down.

rows.label: bf05090100_0150
rows.name: Someone's rather excitable...

rows.label: bf05090100_0155
rows.name: Not like normal Homura.

rows.label: bf05090100_0160
rows.name: Uh, I mean...

rows.label: bf05090100_0170
rows.name: Don't you want to see the place where Rex grew up?

rows.label: bf05090100_0180
rows.name: Hmm, yeah I get what you mean.

rows.label: bf05090100_0190
rows.name:
Actually, that's not a bad idea. That route's
probably one of the safest we could take.

rows.label: bf05090100_0200
rows.name: How about it?

rows.label: bf05090100_0210
rows.name: I'll leave the decision to you, Rex-sama.

rows.label: bf05090100_0220
rows.name:
Then let's do it! We'll head off
as soon as we're ready!

rows.label: bf05090100_0230
rows.name: Yeah!

rows.label: bf05090100_0240
rows.name:
Hey, what are you still doing here,
anyway?

rows.label: bf05090100_0250
rows.name:
I volunteered to come along.
I'm acting as a representative of the Empire.

rows.label: bf05090100_0260
rows.name: Is there a problem?

rows.label: bf05090100_0270
rows.name: No, not at all.

rows.label: bf05090100_0280
rows.name:
The Holy See has extended an
invitation to the Holy Grail.

rows.label: bf05090100_0290
rows.name:
We would not wish to conceal this
information from the other nations.

rows.label: bf05090100_0300
rows.name:
Oh yes, that's the Holy See for you.
Impartial to the very end, eh?

rows.label: bf05090100_0310
rows.name: Indeed.

rows.label: bf05090100_0320
rows.name: That's not a problem for you, is it, Nia?

rows.label: bf05090100_0330
rows.name:
Sure, we're best friends now. I'll get
over her throwing me in jail one day.

rows.label: bf05090100_0340
rows.name:
Now now, my lady, Meleph-sama and 
Kagutsuchi-sama
are on our side.

rows.label: bf05090100_0350
rows.name:
That's much safer than the
alternative.

rows.label: bf05090100_0360
rows.name: Yeah, yeah, I suppose.

rows.label: bf05090100_0370
rows.name: Come on, Nia, lighten up!

rows.label: bf05090100_0380
rows.name:
It was all a big misunderstanding!
They helped us out and everything, remember?

rows.label: bf05090100_0390
rows.name: You're such an idiot sometimes.

rows.label: bf05090100_0400
rows.name: I'm an optimist-

rows.label: bf05090100_0410
rows.name: Call it what you want. You're still an idiot.

rows.label: bf05090100_0420
rows.name: Ugh. Okay, fine. It's water under the bridge.

rows.label: bf05090100_0430
rows.name: Go on! Friends, yeah?

rows.label: bf05090100_0440
rows.name: Heh. Very well. Friends it is.
